      <title>捷克总理敦促反对反对国防支出提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/czech-premier-urges-opposition-to-back-defense-spending-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉（Petr Fiala）呼吁反对派支持更​​高的国防支出，因为地缘政治风险成为议会选举之前的一个有争议的竞选问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/czech-premier-urges-opposition-to-back-defense-spending-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 17:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟救助基金负责人说，市场更喜欢联合债务而不是国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/eu-bailout-fund-chief-says-markets-prefer-joint-debt-for-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲稳定机制董事总经理皮埃尔·格拉梅格纳（Pierre Gramegna）表示，市场认为，欧盟联合联盟借贷而不是扩大各个国家的债务负荷，可以更好地为国防列表提供服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/eu-bailout-fund-chief-says-markets-prefer-joint-debt-for-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 17:56:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利推销2000亿欧元的投资计划来利用私人资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/italy-pitches-200-billion-investment-plan-to-tap-private-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利计划通过欧盟和成员国担保提出一种新的金融工具，以动员数百亿欧元的私人资本和航空航天项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/italy-pitches-200-billion-investment-plan-to-tap-private-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 17:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当华尔街重新考虑销售预测时，特斯拉分享了下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/tesla-shares-plummet-as-wall-street-rethinks-sales-projections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司（Tesla Inc.）的股票正处于自2020年以来最急剧下降的目标，因为华尔街分析师开始削减对车辆运输的估计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/tesla-shares-plummet-as-wall-street-rethinks-sales-projections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 17:19:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加拿大选举的加剧，卡尼开始工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/carney-gets-to-work-in-ottawa-as-election-drumbeat-grows-louder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）开始为加拿大总理迅速接管基础，立法者和内阁部长周一在自由党成员选择他作为新领导人之后举行了关键会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/carney-gets-to-work-in-ottawa-as-election-drumbeat-grows-louder</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 16:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）的《改革》在与埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）支持的竞争对手的争执中陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/nigel-farage-s-reform-uk-stumbles-amid-feud-with-rival-lowe-backed-by-elon-musk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国叛乱改革党在其领导人奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）之间出现崩溃之后，在两个月前吹捧了他的潜在替代者，这是痛苦的内斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/nigel-farage-s-reform-uk-stumbles-amid-feud-with-rival-lowe-backed-by-elon-musk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 15:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰怀疑论者在波兰选举之前获得支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/far-right-candidate-jumps-to-second-in-polish-presidential-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[持怀疑态度的Slawomir Mentzen对居住在波兰的乌克兰人提供支持，在5月的总统投票之前，在最新意见的民意测验中占据了第二名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/far-right-candidate-jumps-to-second-in-polish-presidential-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将审查禁止LGBTQ“转化疗法”的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-will-review-ban-on-lgbtq-conversion-therapy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院同意考虑是否通过禁止有执照的辅导员试图改变儿童的性取向或性别认同来违反宪法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-will-review-ban-on-lgbtq-conversion-therapy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:32:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富裕的大学为保护自己的财富免受税收而奋斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/wealthiest-colleges-fight-to-protect-their-riches-from-taxation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甚至在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他将于周五从哥伦比亚大学（Columbia University）筹集4亿美元的资金，美国最富有的美国大学的官员正在努力与他的政府中的货币萨尔沃（Salvos）作斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/wealthiest-colleges-fight-to-protect-their-riches-from-taxation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
